Package io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasValidator

All Known Implementing Classes:
CompositeValidator, LookupTableNameValidator, NonNullValidator, NotEmptyValidator, PositiveIntegerValidator, StringLengthValidator, StringPatternValidator
public interface AtlasValidator
The interface for validator implementations. Validator has to implement this interface.
